### Learning Modes
- **üìö Flashcards**: Interactive flip cards with text-to-speech
- **‚ùì Quiz**: Multiple choice questions to test your knowledge
- **üí¨ Call & Response**: Type Spanish translations with smart answer validation

### Thematic Regions
